name: Blanco - Nine - Lancero
additionalNotes: Blanco Nine is a full flavored and full bodied cigar with earth, coffee, and spice flavors in the profile. This beautiful cigar is made with Oscuro Corojo wrapper from Nicaragua, Jalapa binder and triple ligero Nicaraguan fillers. A 100% Nicaraguan puro, the name refers to how many attempts were made to reach the perfect blend.
